info.description:
DataTorch Python

DataTorch CLI and Python API libary for programmatic access.

```bash pip install datatorch ``` ## Development ```bash python3 -m pip install --editable . pip3 install -r requirements.txt ``` ### VSCode Configuration #### Formatter Open your VSCode settings, by going `Code -> Preferences -> Settings`. Search for "python formatting provider" and select "black" from the dropdown menu.
